    "# Notes\n",
    "\n",
    "## Expected Runtime (TPU v5e-8)\n",
    "\n",
    "| Model Size | Parallelism | Est. Time |\n",
    "|------------|-------------|-----------|\n",
    "| 3B-4B      | Single core | 10-20 min |\n",
    "| 7B-8B      | Single core | 20-35 min |\n",
    "| 7B-8B      | FSDP (8c)   | 8-15 min  |\n",
    "| 9B-12B     | FSDP (8c)   | 15-30 min |\n",
    "| 14B+       | FSDP (8c)   | 30-60 min |\n",
    "\n",
    "## Memory\n",
    "- TPU v5e: 16GB HBM per core\n",
    "- 8 cores = 128GB total HBM\n",
    "- bfloat16: 2 bytes/param + KV cache + activations\n",
    "- Single core limit: ~8B params comfortably\n",
    "- FSDP shards across cores, enables 70B+ models\n",
    "\n",
    "## Troubleshooting\n",
    "\n",
    "1. **OOM Errors**: Reduce batch size, enable `offload_outputs_to_cpu`\n",
    "2. **Slow compilation**: First run compiles XLA graphs (~5-10 min), subsequent runs faster\n",
    "3. **FSDP issues**: Ensure `torch_xla` version matches PyTorch version\n",
    "4. **Model not found**: Check model ID on Hugging Face Hub\n",
    "\n",
    "## Kaggle-Specific Tips\n",
    "- Enable TPU in Settings → Accelerator → TPU v5e-8\n",
    "- Set \"Internet\" to ON for model downloads\n",
    "- Increase session timeout: Settings → Execution → 30+ hours\n",
    "- Use `/kaggle/working` for outputs (persists after session)\n",
    "- Check GPU/TPU usage in the Resources panel\n"
   ]
  }
